casebody.data:
Friday, January 18, 2002

DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

01-1829. Columbus Bar Assn. v. Milless.

This matter is pending before the court upon the filing by respondent, Charles Keller Milless, on December 7, 2001, of a motion to supplement the record. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by this court that the motion to supplement the record be, and hereby is, granted.

Cook, J., dissents.
